{"id": "1193520238134833243", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "906028080462692372", "author_name": "zhuxiangfng", "author_bot": false, "content": "请问一下，有谁知道珊的个人剧情的最后一章的结局是什么意思吗？我没看太懂。", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T11:43:19.305000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1193521499886338068", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "456226577798135808", "author_name": "Deleted User", "author_bot": false, "content": "是被受克蘇鲁感召而“瘋”了的艺术家，前往海洋深處的“新家”", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T11:48:20.130000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["906028080462692372"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1193520238134833243", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1193522400474701864", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "906028080462692372", "author_name": "zhuxiangfng", "author_bot": false, "content": "女仆最后是被珊做成雕塑了吗？珊为什么要说女仆早就死了呀？", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T11:51:54.847000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["456226577798135808"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1193521499886338068", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1193526336598319115", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "456226577798135808", "author_name": "Deleted User", "author_bot": false, "content": "1、是的\n2、這個不清楚", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T12:07:33.292000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["906028080462692372"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1193522400474701864", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1193528355291664535", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "906028080462692372", "author_name": "zhuxiangfng", "author_bot": false, "content": "后面珊能说出守密人真正的名字也挺奇怪的。反正她的故事写得云里雾里的，不知道以后有没有剧情补充。", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T12:15:34.586000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["456226577798135808"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1193526336598319115", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1193530212902776932", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "456226577798135808", "author_name": "Deleted User", "author_bot": false, "content": "守密人與喚醒體之間靈與心的共振，使得守密人進入了喚醒體的夢。所以這段故事全部都是發生在夢裡的。是一場守密人和珊共同親歷的夢，也是一種“正史”的“if線”——現實中，珊為了追求美，使用融蝕漿製作雕塑，引發“雕塑殺人案”，而侍女卡米耶亦因此喪命。珊本人沉迷於以融蝕漿製作雕塑，最後也死去，後成為喚醒體，與守密人相識相知，兩人之間產生共振，就有了這場夢。\n這段劇情裡，珊從一開始就知道這是夢境，也第一眼就認出了卡米耶身體裡是守密人。但她傾心於守密人的美，滿懷著愛意和熱情推動自己的劇本，渴望將守密人做成真正的雕塑「珊瑚女之死」。這既是她對於美的追求，也是她對守密人熾熱情感的展現。", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T12:22:57.475000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["906028080462692372"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1193528355291664535", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1193530828521734154", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "456226577798135808", "author_name": "Deleted User", "author_bot": false, "content": "2、關於女僕為什麼早就死了，因為珊是用融蝕漿去雕刻雕像，因為一旦被融蝕漿沾染上，本身就代表你已經死了", "timestamp": "2024-01-07T12:25:24.250000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["906028080462692372"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1193522400474701864", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
